.SH "NAME"
halreport \- creates a report on the status of the HAL
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBhalreport\fR [\fIoutfilename\fR]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
\fBhalreport\fR
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04' 1.\h'+01'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP "  1." 4.2
.\}
Supports components made by halcompile and numerous legacy components
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04' 2.\h'+01'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP "  2." 4.2
.\}
Known unhandled components:
.PP
at_pid
.RS 4
naming conflicts with pid, seldom used
.RE
.PP
boss_plc
.RS 4
no manpage or docs (any users?)
.RE
.PP
watchdog
.RS 4
seldom used (no users in\-tree)
.RE
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04' 3.\h'+01'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP "  3." 4.2
.\}
Deprecated/obsolete components:
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
counter
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
supply
.RE
.RE
.sp
Identification of functions used according to pin name\&. Default handling works for components that:
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04' 1.\h'+01'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP "  1." 4.2
.\}
use names=|count= (\&.comp components created with halcompile)
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04' 2.\h'+01'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP "  2." 4.2
.\}
have a
\fBsingle\fR
function
.RE
.sp
